    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "Do cold starts matter for production?",
      "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Yes, especially for Replicate (5-30s) and Fireworks (1-3s). Cerebras and Groq have no cold start because models stay warm on dedicated hardware. If your traffic is spiky, choose providers with low cold-start times." }
